title: Australothelais demarzi
text: Australothelais demarzi is a species of <a href="beetle">beetle</a> in the family <a href="Cerambycidae">Cerambycidae</a>. It was described by <a href="Stephan%20von%20Breuning%20%28entomologist%29">Breuning</a> in 1963. It is known from <a href="Australia">Australia</a>.
